title: East Side - 1 Bedroom Apartment
posting_body: Special NOT included in the listed price!
Brand new complex east of Mueller.
Come be the first to live in your unit.
Near Springdale Rd, gain quick access to Mueller, East Austin, and Hwy 183.
Brand new unit with high quality finishes such as 9ft+ ceilings, hard plank flooring, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and full sized washer and dryer.
Entertain guests in the clubroom with TVs, a kitchen with island, coffee bar, and billiards.
Escape the Texas heat with a private cabana next to the pool.
"I am a Realtor/apartment locator in the Austin area.
My services are 100% free, don’t hesitate to give me a call.
If you'd like to learn more about this property, or would like to review other available options, call/text or email me.
Also at Grackle Realty, if looking to buy, we focus on educating renters on how to become home owners.
Follow us on our Instagram to learn more!
*I strive to keep my postings up to date, but pricing and availability are both subject to change.*"
